TEXT.S: = Isaetipan pahikukian = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Ciansyang ka alang Isaetipan pahikukian. 1,927 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 5,066 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 25% niqan 1,247 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 75% niqan 3,819 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis 20%, Truku 2%, Tayal 1%, Bunun 1%.
